doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='About Ali Bińkowska - AI Training & HRTech Innovation')
        meta(name='author', content='Ali Bińkowska')

        title About Me - Ali Bińkowska

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')
        include includes/css.pug

    body.d-flex.flex-column.h-100.bg-white
        main.flex-shrink-0
            include includes/navbar.pug

            // Page Header
            .container.px-5.my-5
                .text-center.mb-5
                    h2.display-5.fw-bolder
                        span.text-gradient.d-inline About Me
                
                .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-11.col-xl-9.col-xxl-8
                        
                        // About Me Card
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5

                                p.lead.fw-light.mb-4 I've always looked for ways to make work easier and eliminate repetition. When I understand something well, sharing it feels natural.
                                p.lead.fw-light.mb-0 Years working abroad and collaborating with international teams - across large corporations and small organizations - shaped how I think.
                                p.lead.fw-light.mb-4 My technical background adds another layer: I understand both the business side and how things actually work under the hood.
                                p.lead.fw-light.mb-4 Creating my first Udemy course revealed how much I enjoyed this work. I continued with more courses and technical webinars for AI master's program at WSKZ.
                                p.lead.fw-light.mb-0 My approach: grasp the underlying principles, not just the surface-level how-to. Be someone who can judge what makes sense, not just execute what's trending. That's how you make smart AI decisions for your specific situation.

                        // Current Focus Card
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5
                                .d-flex.align-items-center.mb-4
                                    .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary.text-white.rounded-3.me-3
                                        i.bi.bi-lightning-fill
                                    h3.fw-bolder.mb-0 Current Focus

                                .row.row-cols-1.row-cols-md-2.g-4
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-start.bg-light.rounded-4.p-4.h-100
                                            .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary.text-white.rounded-3.me-3
                                                i.bi.bi-rocket-takeoff
                                            div
                                                h5.fw-bold.mb-2 HRTech Startup
                                                p.mb-0 Building innovative solutions for modern human resources challenges
                                    .col
                                        .d-flex.align-items-start.bg-light.rounded-4.p-4.h-100
                                            .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary.text-white.rounded-3.me-3
                                                i.bi.bi-mortarboard
                                            div
                                                h5.fw-bold.mb-2 AI Educator
                                                p.mb-0 Training professionals through webinars, Udemy courses, and direct consulting with businesses

                        // Divider
                        .pb-5

                        // Connect Card
                        .card.shadow.border-0.rounded-4.mb-5
                            .card-body.p-5.text-center
                                p.lead.fw-light.mb-4 Interested in working together or learning more?
                                .d-flex.justify-content-center.gap-4.fs-2.mb-4
                                    a.text-gradient(href='https://linkedin.com/in/alibinkowska', target='_blank', title='LinkedIn')
                                        i.bi.bi-linkedin
                                    a.text-gradient(href='https://x.com/AliBinkowska', target='_blank', title='Twitter/X')
                                        i.bi.bi-twitter
                                    a.text-gradient(href='https://medium.com/@alibinkowska', target='_blank', title='Medium')
                                        i.bi.bi-medium
                                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.px-5.py-3(href='contact.html') Get In Touch

        include includes/footer.pug
        include includes/scripts.pug
